Constructor for the FNG (feature neighborhood graph) S4 object

create_FNG_object.Rd

Creates the FID object and populates its subfields

Usage

create_FNG_object(
  id = NA_character_,
  dataset_id = NA_character_,
  filepath = NA_character_,
  accessor = NA_character_,
  parent_id = NA_character_,
  record_id = NA_character_,
  edge_metric = NA_character_,
  metric_type = NA_character_
)

Arguments

id

Main ID of MAMS object

dataset_id

Parent dataset ID

filepath

Path to the data file

accessor

Accessor

parent_id

Parent FNG object

record_id

Record ID

edge_metric

Type of edge metric used

metric_type

Details of the edge metric

Value

a FNG S4 object for use with MAMS
